 anonymously. No login required.\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"InstaPvStory - Anonymous Instagram Story &amp; Profile Viewer\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"View Instagram stories, posts, followers and highlights anonymously. No login required.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"app-wrapper\" style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:100vh\"><header class=\"Header-module__85i50G__header\"><div class=\"Header-module__85i50G__inner\"><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__logo\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"Header-module__85i50G__logoIcon\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.95\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.8\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__logoText\">InstaPvStory</span></a><nav class=\"Header-module__85i50G__nav\"><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__navLink \" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__navLink \" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__navLink Header-module__85i50G__active\" href=\"/features\">Features</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__navLink \" href=\"/about\">About</a><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__divider\"></span><button class=\"Header-module__85i50G__loginBtn\"><svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\"></path></svg>Login</button></nav><button class=\"Header-module__85i50G__hamburger \" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__hamburgerLine\"></span><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__hamburgerLine\"></span><span class=\"Header-module__85i50G__hamburgerLine\"></span></button></div></header><div class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileMenu \" role=\"navigation\"><nav class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLinks\"><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLink \" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLink \" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLink Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLinkActive\" href=\"/features\">Features</a><a class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileNavLink \" href=\"/about\">About</a></nav><div class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileDivider\"></div><button class=\"Header-module__85i50G__mobileLoginBtn\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\"></path></svg>Login</button></div><main style=\"flex:1\"><main class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__featuresPage\"><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__container\"><nav class=\"Breadcrumb-module__U9IJfG__breadcrumb\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\"><ol class=\"Breadcrumb-module__U9IJfG__list\"><li class=\"Breadcrumb-module__U9IJfG__item\"><a class=\"Breadcrumb-module__U9IJfG__link\" href=\"/\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\"></path><polyline points=\"9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22\"></polyline></svg>Home</a></li><li class=\"Breadcrumb-module__U9IJfG__item\"><span class=\"Breadcrumb-module__U9IJfG__sep\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\"></polyline></svg></span><span class=\"Breadcrumb-module__U9IJfG__current\" aria-current=\"page\">Features</span></li></ol></nav><header class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__header\"><span class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__badge\">Capabilities</span><h1 class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__title\">The Power of <span class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__grad\">InstaPvStory</span></h1></header><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__grid\"><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__featureCard\" style=\"--acc:#7c3aed\"><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__icon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path><path d=\"M12 8v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 16h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardTitle\">100% Anonymous</h3><p class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardDesc\">Browse any public Instagram profile without ever logging in. Your identity stays completely hidden — no traces, no footprints left on the viewer list.</p></div><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__featureCard\" style=\"--acc:#06b6d4\"><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__icon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"></polygon></svg></div><h3 class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardTitle\">Instant Results</h3><p class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardDesc\">Our optimized architecture fetches real-time data in milliseconds. Experience zero-lag browsing even with high-resolution media.</p></div><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__featureCard\" style=\"--acc:#f59e0b\"><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__icon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polygon points=\"10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8\"></polygon></svg></div><h3 class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardTitle\">Stories &amp; Reels</h3><p class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardDesc\">Watch full stories and play reels with full audio support. Access the complete public feed of any professional account instantly.</p></div><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__featureCard\" style=\"--acc:#10b981\"><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__icon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"11\" width=\"18\" height=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardTitle\">Zero Login Required</h3><p class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardDesc\">We prioritize your security by never asking for your credentials. Protect your personal account while conducting research or browsing.</p></div><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__featureCard\" style=\"--acc:#ec4899\"><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__icon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"2\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"12\"></line><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardTitle\">Worldwide Fetch</h3><p class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardDesc\">Bypass regional restrictions and view public profiles from anywhere in the world through our global proxy network.</p></div><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__featureCard\" style=\"--acc:#8b5cf6\"><div class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__icon\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"></path><polyline points=\"22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01\"></polyline></svg></div><h3 class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardTitle\">Advanced Discovery Engine</h3><p class=\"features-module__eU_uXa__cardDesc\">Unlike simple scrapers, we use high-performance discovery protocols that ensure data accuracy and compliance with public information standards.</p></div></div></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__footer\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__content\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__brand\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__brandTitle\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__logoIcon\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"4\" fill=\"white\" opacity=\"0.95\"></circle><path d=\"M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.8\"></path></svg></div><h3 style=\"color:#ffffff;margin:0\">InstaPvStory</h3></div><p class=\"text-small\">Anonymous Instagram story and highlight viewer.</p></div><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__links\"><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__group\"><h4>Company</h4><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/features\">Features</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></div><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__group\"><h4>Legal</h4><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/disclaimer\">Disclaimer</a></div><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__group\"><h4>Support</h4><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a><a class=\"text-small\" href=\"/#faq\">FAQ</a></div></div></div><div class=\"Footer-module__hP-FLq__bottom\"><p class=\"text-small\">© <!-- -->2024<!-- --> InstaPvStory. All rights reserved.</p></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0yb2wil16uz6h.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[68504,[\\\"/_next/st